transforms.code:
FROM    (
            SELECT  clearing_code
                    ,asset_flux_id
                    ,gmt_accounting
                    ,transaction_amt
                    ,transaction_type
                    ,recon_status
                    ,biz_product_code
            FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_ren_acc_item_default_pt
            WHERE   year <= SUBSTR('20250802',1,4) 
        ) t1
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
                    SELECT  DISTINCT clearing_code
                            ,FIRST_VALUE(merchant_name) OVER (PARTITION BY clearing_code ORDER BY modified_at ) AS clearing_description 
                            ,trans_acc_desc AS account_description 
                            ,trans_acc_no AS account_no 
                            ,CASE   WHEN payable_receivable = 'payable' THEN 'C'
                                    WHEN payable_receivable = 'receivable' THEN 'D'
                            END AS direction 
                            ,codes AS product_category 
                            ,brand
                            ,type_cc AS bank_or_nonbank 
                            ,groupings AS grouping 
                    FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.ods_clearing_code_mapping
                    WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                ) t2
ON      t1.clearing_code = t2.clearing_code

FROM    (
            SELECT  txn_date
                    ,clearing_code
                    ,clearing_description
                    ,account_description
                    ,account_no
                    ,direction
                    ,product_category
                    ,currency
                    ,COALESCE(ROUND((SUM(transaction_amt) / 100),2),0) AS transaction_amt
                    ,COUNT(DISTINCT IF(fund_status IN ('REFUND','PAYMENT_CANCEL','WITHDRAW_CANCEL','WITHDRAW_REFUND'),acct_asset_flux_id,NULL)) AS number_of_transactions_cancel
                    ,COUNT(DISTINCT IF(fund_status IN ('PAYMENT','WITHDRAW'),acct_asset_flux_id,NULL)) AS number_of_transactions_success
                    ,brand
                    ,bank_or_nonbank
                    ,groupings
            FROM    (
                        SELECT  SUBSTR(gmt_accounting,1,10) AS txn_date
                                ,clearing_code
                                ,clearing_description
                                ,account_description
                                ,account_no
                                ,direction
                                ,product_category
                                ,currency
                                ,fund_status
                                ,acct_asset_flux_id
                                ,CASE   WHEN fund_status IN ('REFUND','PAYMENT_CANCEL','WITHDRAW_CANCEL','WITHDRAW_REFUND') THEN transaction_amt * (
                                                    -1
                                        )
                                        WHEN fund_status IN ('PAYMENT','WITHDRAW') THEN transaction_amt
                                        ELSE 0
                                END AS transaction_amt
                                ,brand
                                ,bank_or_nonbank
                                ,groupings
                        FROM    dana_cloud_dwh.dwd_acct_clearing_report_v2_dd
                        WHERE   dt = '20250802'
                    ) t1
            GROUP BY txn_date
                     ,clearing_code
                     ,clearing_description
                     ,account_description
                     ,account_no
                     ,direction
                     ,product_category
                     ,currency
                     ,brand
                     ,bank_or_nonbank
                     ,groupings
        ) t2
